    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the culture of the Rappahannock, a tribe of Native Americans in Virginia who inhabit an area stretching from the Northern Neck on the Rappahannock River to the Mattaponi Rivers and as far north as Fredericksburg, Virginia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047316/Rappahannock Tribe [online] (2005)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refierese a la cultura del Rappahannock, una tribu de los americanos nativos en Virginia que habitan un área del cuello norteño entre el río de Rappahannock y los ríos de Mattaponi.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de cultuur van de Rappahannock, een Amerikaanse indianenstam uit Virginia die een gebied bewoont dat het gebied omvat van Northern Neck tussen de rivier de Rappahannock en de rivier de Mattaponi, tot aan Fredericksburg, Virginia, in het noorden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指拉帕漢諾克族之文化，為維吉尼亞州之美洲原住民族，分佈範圍從帕漢諾克河沿線之北領（Northern Neck）地區至瑪塔波尼河（Mattaponi Rivers），最北遠及維吉尼亞州的弗雷德里克斯堡（Fredericksburg)。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
